we do have a say in.

2271
02:37:33,653 --> 02:37:37,491
And that's how we kill this bitch.

2272
02:37:39,034 --> 02:37:41,786
And I say shooting's too good for her.

2273
02:37:41,953 --> 02:37:47,834
John Ruth could've shot her
anywhere anytime along the way.

2274
02:37:48,001 --> 02:37:52,881
But John Ruth was The Hangman.

2275
02:37:53,048 --> 02:37:54,966
And when The Hangman catches you,

2276
02:37:55,133 --> 02:37:58,636
you don't die by no bullet.

2277
02:37:58,804 --> 02:38:02,974
When The Hangman catches you,
you hang.

2278
02:38:03,141 --> 02:38:06,269
"You only need to hang mean bastards..."

2279
02:38:07,938 --> 02:38:11,483
"...but mean bastards, you need to hang."

2280
02:38:34,381 --> 02:38:38,176
As my first and final act

2281
02:38:38,343 --> 02:38:41,429
as the sheriff of Red Rock,

2282
02:38:41,596 --> 02:38:44,307
I sentence you, Domergue,

2283
02:38:44,474 --> 02:38:47,727
to hang by the neck until death!

2284
02:39:02,534 --> 02:39:04,327
Hang on, Daisy.

2285
02:39:04,494 --> 02:39:06,580
I want to watch.

2286
02:39:41,072 --> 02:39:44,075
Now, that was a nice dance.

2287
02:39:45,952 --> 02:39:49,039
That sure was pretty.

2288
02:39:53,543 --> 02:39:54,923
Shit!

2289
02:40:41,591 --> 02:40:43,093
Hey.

2290
02:40:45,136 --> 02:40:47,514
Can I see that Lincoln letter?

2291
02:41:30,306 --> 02:41:33,726
"Dear Marquis,

2292
02:41:33,893 --> 02:41:37,021
"I hope this letter finds you

2293
02:41:37,188 --> 02:41:41,442
"in good health and stead.

2294
02:41:41,609 --> 02:41:44,070
"I'm doing fine,

2295
02:41:44,237 --> 02:41:49,117
"although I wish
there were more hours in a day.

2296
02:41:49,284 --> 02:41:52,662
"There's just so much to do.

2297
02:41:52,829 --> 02:41:57,250
"Times are changing slowly but surely,

2298
02:41:57,417 --> 02:42:02,380
"and it's men like you
that will make a difference.

2299
02:42:02,547 --> 02:42:08,761
"Your military success
is a credit not only to you,

2300
02:42:08,928 --> 02:42:11,889
"but your race as well.

2301
02:42:12,057 --> 02:42:17,520
"I'm very proud
every time I hear news of you.

2302
02:42:17,687 --> 02:42:21,774
"We still have a long way to go,

2303
02:42:21,941 --> 02:42:28,406
"but hand in hand,
I know we will get there.

2304
02:42:28,573 --> 02:42:33,828
"I just want to let you know
you're in my thoughts.

2305
02:42:33,995 --> 02:42:39,292
"Hopefully,
our paths will cross in the future.

2306
02:42:39,459 --> 02:42:46,424
"Until then, I remain your friend.

2307
02:42:46,591 --> 02:42:49,510
"Ole Mary Todd's calling,

2308
02:42:49,677 --> 02:42:55,266
"so I guess it must be time for bed.

2309
02:42:55,433 --> 02:43:00,396
Respectfully, Abraham Lincoln."

2310
02:43:04,317 --> 02:43:06,527
"Ole Mary Todd."

2311
02:43:06,694 --> 02:43:08,988
That's a nice touch.

2312
02:43:09,155 --> 02:43:11,574
Yeah.

2313
02:43:11,741 --> 02:43:13,701
Thanks.
